tweet: Numerous explanations for why Warriors kept coming back vs Blazers: Strength in numbers, heart of a champion, Steph and Dray going off, Looney crashing boards, etc. Perhaps most under heralded: Conditioning. Warriors ran circles around Blazers to close every one of those games.
